{"tid":699049,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"承建商為三星、新昌聯營","createTime":"2018-06-12T07:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T12:09:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a925eb226e8f666dc54290efe2a894320aed1fa2","tid":699049,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180612/20417968\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180612%2F20417968&d=7bvCyS3Dl2SPdSt2SwHmwdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=aacccf4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180612%2F20417968&h=b4ab8d2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180612/20417968</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月12日 <br />\n<br />\n承建商為三星、新昌聯營<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180612/large/12la4p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180612%2Flarge%2F12la4p5.jpg&h=75020eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡健鴻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵沙中綫工程再爆醜聞，涉事土瓜灣站的承建商為三星──新昌聯營公司，於2012年取得有關工程合約，負責建造九龍城段車站及隧道工程，即土瓜灣站、宋皇臺站以及連接至何文田站的1,600米隧道，合約總值45.69億元。股東三星物產為韓資公司，參與本港多項大型基建工程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新昌曾參與建高鐵<br />\n<br />\n另一股東新昌集團控股有限公司為本港上市，執行董事兼行政總裁為香港工程師學會前任會長蔡健鴻。新昌曾參與沙中綫南北走廊前期工程、南港島綫黃竹坑鐵路維修車廠、高鐵香港段皇崗至米埔隧道等。<br />\n<br />\n公司註冊處資料顯示，三星物產香港由韓國Samsung C&amp;T Corporation持有99.99%股份，其餘股份由一名叫金燦武（KIM CHAN MOO）的人持有，公司董事為金燦武及洪淳勝（HONG SOONSEUNG），二人均持有香港身份證。新昌2017年報顯示，三星──新昌為在香港經營的非法團共同經營業務，新昌參股40%。<br />\n<br />\n三星物產參與多項本港基建工程，今年初三星與本港承建商利基控股合組聯營公司，投得東涌新市鎮擴展－填海及前期工程合約，合約價值達120.76億元；2016年亦曾與利基控股投得機場三跑初期填海項目達28億元工程合約。<br />\n<br />\n■記者趙雅婷  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n削筋後無補救　落石屎掩飾<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n馬時亨：樂意退位讓賢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n削筋後無補救　落石屎掩飾<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨：樂意退位讓賢<br />\n<br />\n沙中綫工程再爆豆腐渣醜聞雙重鋼筋削走一半　土瓜灣站豎危牆"},{"pid":"cca456ac2541fa5d16fde46340f9af7aec264aa0","tid":699049,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e8f126294e8e81ce8b554b31491689e1d2afef","tid":699049,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"046b728c72d2c38bf47f74942d868a53c76666b2","tid":699049,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T10:04:28.000Z","msg":"三星好似做緊3rd runway dcm&hellip;"},{"pid":"01d52c8527450bab6ea1b4433339a8984644a890","tid":699049,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55e8f126294e8e81ce8b554b31491689e1d2afef","tid":699049,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T10:27:28.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n不過買電視有得送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462ec5acc6be269530ae57bddf6e154531b0f172","tid":699049,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T10:29:44.000Z","msg":"三星又多飯數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3429c93003ea51cf40f115eabc87db00b64ef29","tid":699049,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"新昌反正就嚟收皮,乜都瀨晒落佢度"},{"pid":"35529bca0d78528d9e5aa9dbcda3dc37bf0377b4","tid":699049,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:31:09.000Z","msg":"Shamesung"},{"pid":"2930dbfa806c5ae1a04dfe85aa849622de70055d","tid":699049,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:09:56.000Z","msg":"Joseph Choi條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkg